Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是冰凉的 干燥的 荒凉的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's cold, it's dry, it's desolated,
