Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他不是个好地方 如果你正好在那里 不会喜欢它的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's not a nice place, you wouldn't enjoy it, if you're right there 
