Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明火星极地固态水的存在 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the existence of water ice at the martian poles 
